name: Check suggestions when using autocomplete on input field
fullName: features/ui/widget_interactions_with_input_fields.feature#Check suggestions when using autocomplete on input field

steps.name: I navigate to Demoqa Home page
Given I navigate to the Auto Complete page
When I type "Bl" in the field
Then I see "Blue" and "Black" in my suggestions
And the selected suggestion is added to the field

labels.name: suite
labels.value: Check suggestions when using autocomplete on input field
